org.sakaiproject.genericdao.base
Class BaseGenericDao

java.lang.Object
  org.sakaiproject.genericdao.base.BaseGenericDao
All Implemented Interfaces:
GenericDao, BasicModifier
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseBasicGenericDao
public abstract class BaseGenericDao
extends Object
implements GenericDao

This is the simple base implementation which includes shared methods and should be extended, this handles the caching checks and the interceptors on the basic methods

Author:
Aaron Zeckoski (azeckoski@gmail.com)
